00:18:56,299 --> 00:18:57,420
Does this count as proof?

576
00:18:57,660 --> 00:18:59,539
That proves you abandoned her!

577
00:19:00,460 --> 00:19:00,859
She...

578
00:19:00,859 --> 00:19:02,740
She went back to her country heartbroken!

579
00:19:03,119 --> 00:19:04,680
Not back to her country.

580
00:19:05,059 --> 00:19:06,500
She went abroad.

581
00:19:06,500 --> 00:19:08,480
My ex-wife is Chinese.

582
00:19:09,339 --> 00:19:10,059
Chinese?

583
00:19:10,059 --> 00:19:10,779
Yes.

584
00:19:10,900 --> 00:19:13,099
That proves even more that you abandoned her!

585
00:19:13,099 --> 00:19:15,819
She left her homeland for Germany!

586
00:19:16,140 --> 00:19:16,619
No.

587
00:19:17,400 --> 00:19:18,900
She wanted to go to Germany.

588
00:19:19,160 --> 00:19:20,660
I wanted to stay in China.

589
00:19:20,779 --> 00:19:21,339
So...

590
00:19:21,559 --> 00:19:22,519
we broke up.

591
00:19:23,339 --> 00:19:24,700
You're really strange too.

592
00:19:24,700 --> 00:19:25,819
You, a foreigner...

593
00:19:25,980 --> 00:19:26,740
why are you so dead set on

594
00:19:26,740 --> 00:19:28,180
staying in our China?

595
00:19:28,380 --> 00:19:29,339
China is good.

596
00:19:29,579 --> 00:19:30,579
I love China.

597
00:19:31,319 --> 00:19:31,859
Good.

598
00:19:34,900 --> 00:19:36,660
I don't have time for an interview right now.

599
00:19:39,240 --> 00:19:39,900
Jingjing.

600
00:19:40,539 --> 00:19:41,500
Is it really you?

601
00:19:42,500 --> 00:19:44,660
What made you think of calling Dad?

602
00:19:47,700 --> 00:19:48,500
No...

603
00:19:49,180 --> 00:19:49,940
It's not that...

604
00:19:49,940 --> 00:19:50,339
You...

605
00:19:50,539 --> 00:19:51,759
Listen to my explanation.

606
00:19:52,460 --> 00:19:54,059
That was all made up by reporters.

607
00:19:54,059 --> 00:19:55,380
I didn't say it.

608
00:19:55,859 --> 00:19:56,859
You must absolutely...

609
00:19:58,619 --> 00:19:59,619
There's a recording?

610
00:20:00,220 --> 00:20:02,059
The reporters faked that recording.

611
00:20:03,819 --> 00:20:05,059
There's footage of me too?

612
00:20:06,140 --> 00:20:08,220
The reporters faked that footage.

613
00:20:08,700 --> 00:20:10,180
You must not believe it.

614
00:20:10,880 --> 00:20:11,240
Then...

615
00:20:11,460 --> 00:20:11,819
Then...

616
00:20:11,920 --> 00:20:13,160
Then what do you want Dad to do?

617
00:20:13,619 --> 00:20:14,119
How about...

618
00:20:14,339 --> 00:20:14,940
Dad...

619
00:20:15,460 --> 00:20:16,079
issues a...

620
00:20:16,240 --> 00:20:16,819
statement?

621
00:20:18,140 --> 00:20:19,859
Or Dad holds a...

622
00:20:20,579 --> 00:20:21,660
press conference?

623
00:20:23,559 --> 00:20:25,500
Or Dad gives himself two big slaps?

624
00:20:26,240 --> 00:20:26,779
You...

625
00:20:27,440 --> 00:20:28,019
Jingjing.

626
00:20:28,880 --> 00:20:30,420
As long as you still acknowledge this dad...

627
00:20:30,700 --> 00:20:31,880
whatever you want me to do...

628
00:20:32,200 --> 00:20:33,240
I'll agree to it all.

629
00:20:34,359 --> 00:20:34,980
You...

630
00:20:39,819 --> 00:20:41,259
Aunties, let's do it again.

631
00:20:41,680 --> 00:20:44,759
One, two, three, four.

632
00:20:45,160 --> 00:20:48,400
Five, six, seven, eight.

633
00:20:48,759 --> 00:20:51,839
Two, two, three, four.

634
00:20:52,160 --> 00:20:55,119
Five, six, seven, eight.

635
00:20:55,359 --> 00:20:56,279
Just like that.

636
00:20:56,279 --> 00:20:57,119
That should be enough, right?

637
00:20:57,559 --> 00:20:59,079
It doesn't seem very synchronized yet.

638
00:20:59,519 --> 00:21:00,119
Then how about...

639
00:21:00,119 --> 00:21:00,799
How about we do two more?

640
00:21:00,799 --> 00:21:01,519
Old Liang.

641
00:21:02,720 --> 00:21:03,799
I'm really sorry.

642
00:21:04,279 --> 00:21:05,880
I misunderstood you before.

643
00:21:06,160 --> 00:21:07,279
Misunderstood me about what?

644
00:21:07,279 --> 00:21:08,880
I thought you were always bragging.

645
00:21:08,880 --> 00:21:10,359
I didn't believe the big star Bai Jingjing...

646
00:21:10,359 --> 00:21:11,559
...was really your daughter.

647
00:21:13,400 --> 00:21:14,720
You believe it now, right?

648
00:21:15,279 --> 00:21:16,640
Well, that's partly your fault.

649
00:21:16,880 --> 00:21:18,680
You usually talk way too big.

650
00:21:18,680 --> 00:21:20,200
Three parts truth, seven parts fake.

651
00:21:20,200 --> 00:21:21,079
Full of hot air.

652
00:21:21,480 --> 00:21:22,799
Who? Who is?

653
00:21:23,440 --> 00:21:24,240
In the past...

654
00:21:24,240 --> 00:21:26,160
...I won't blame you since you didn't know.

655
00:21:26,319 --> 00:21:27,960
But now that you know...

656
00:21:27,960 --> 00:21:30,119
...that I am Bai Jingjing's biological father...

657
00:21:30,200 --> 00:21:31,599
...why are you still so rude?

658
00:21:31,839 --> 00:21:33,319
Shake the star's dad's hand first.

659
00:21:34,480 --> 00:21:36,319
So Bai Jingjing really is your daughter?

660
00:21:36,559 --> 00:21:37,480
Then why has she...

661
00:21:37,480 --> 00:21:38,920
...never come to Yangliu Xincheng...

662
00:21:38,920 --> 00:21:40,079
...to visit you?

663
00:21:40,400 --> 00:21:41,000
She...

664
00:21:41,440 --> 00:21:42,640
She's busy.

665
00:21:42,839 --> 00:21:45,960
Being a big star these days is so busy.

666
00:21:46,119 --> 00:21:47,000
Her daily schedule...

667
00:21:47,000 --> 00:21:48,839
...is packed absolutely full.

668
00:21:49,039 --> 00:21:50,200
You could say...

669
00:21:50,400 --> 00:21:51,920
...she gets up in the middle of the night...

670
00:21:51,920 --> 00:21:53,539
...and comes back at sundown.

671
00:21:53,960 --> 00:21:55,539
She's too busy.

672
00:21:56,799 --> 00:21:57,920
But no matter how busy...

673
00:21:58,720 --> 00:22:00,960
...she should make time to see you.

674
00:22:00,960 --> 00:22:01,839
Exactly.

675
00:22:02,019 --> 00:22:02,720
She'll come.

676
00:22:02,759 --> 00:22:04,000
She'll definitely come.

677
00:22:04,240 --> 00:22:05,200
You just watch.

678
00:22:05,240 --> 00:22:06,039
Any day now...

679
00:22:06,039 --> 00:22:07,160
...she'll definitely come.

680
00:22:07,599 --> 00:22:08,720
She should be coming to see me.

681
00:22:08,799 --> 00:22:10,680
Good.

682
00:22:14,319 --> 00:22:14,859
Miss Bai.

683
00:22:14,859 --> 00:22:16,920
May I ask when your next project is?

684
00:22:17,059 --> 00:22:18,359
When do you plan to get married?

685
00:22:18,359 --> 00:22:19,799
When is your next project?
